commitMessage:
Added Connman VPN Connection Interface Code

The patch contain following major API's changes:
  1. GList *vpn_get_connections(void);
  2. struct vpn_connection *vpn_get_connection(
                const char *host, const char *domain);
  3. enum connman_lib_err vpn_connection_clear_property(
                struct vpn_connection *connection);
  4. enum connman_lib_err vpn_connection_connect(
                struct vpn_connection *connection,
                connman_lib_reply_cb callback,
                void *user_data);
  5. enum connman_lib_err vpn_connection_disconnect(
                struct vpn_connection *connection);

The code also contains the Signals & Property Changed
updation logic by listening to the D-Bus Signals.

